Once opon a time in a forest there lived a monkey who resided on a jamun tree which was on the bank of the river.
In the same forest there lived a crocodile and his wife.
On day the crocodile came to the bank's of the river and rested under the kind herted monkey offered him some fruits the crocodile came back the next day for more fruits as he love them. As day passed by the crocodile and monkey become good friends.
